data.name: ReadControlTable1
data.value: select top(1) CNTL_TBL_ID, LAST_USED_NUMBER from CKT_CONTROL_TABLE where CNTL_TBL_ID = 'OUTBOUND EFT NUMBER'

data.name: ReadControlTable2
data.value: select top(1) CNTL_TBL_ID, LAST_USED_NUMBER from CKT_CONTROL_TABLE where CNTL_TBL_ID = 'OUTBOUND EFT TRACE NUMBER'

data.name: ReadCsePersonCsePersonAccountDisbursementTransaction
data.value: select CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, DISB_TRAN_ID, TYPE, AMOUNT, PROCESS_DATE, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATE_TMST, DISBURSEMENT_DATE, CASH_NON_CASH_IND, RECAPTURED_IND, COLLECTION_DATE, DBT_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND, EXCESS_URA_IND from CKT_DISB_TRAN where (PROCESS_DATE = @processDate) and (TYPE = @type) and (INTERSTATE_IND = 'N') and (DBT_GENERATED_ID is not null) order by CSP_NUMBER, DISBURSEMENT_DATE

data.name: ReadDisbursementStatusHistoryDisbursementStatus
data.value: select top(1) DBS_GENERATED_ID, DTR_GENERATED_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, DISB_STAT_HIST_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REASON_TEXT from CKT_DISB_STAT_HIST where (@dtrGeneratedId = DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc, CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadDisbursementType
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TYPE_ID, CODE from CKT_DISB_TYPE where DISB_TYPE_ID = @disbTypeId

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PROCESS_DATE, AMOUNT, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, DP_CSE_PER_NUM, CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, IMPREST_FUND_CODE, CLASSIFICATION, TYPE, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: UpdateControlTable1
data.value: update CKT_CONTROL_TABLE set LAST_USED_NUMBER = @lastUsedNumber where CNTL_TBL_ID = @cntlTblId

data.name: UpdateControlTable2
data.value: update CKT_CONTROL_TABLE set LAST_USED_NUMBER = @lastUsedNumber where CNTL_TBL_ID = @cntlTblId
